      <title>马杜罗感到羞辱和愤怒，在执政期间最严厉的镇压下关押了 2,000 名委内瑞拉人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-08-04/humiliated-by-machado-maduro-arrests-2-000-in-crackdown-of-venezuela-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉的社会主义政权在经过激烈的选举后努力维持权力，因此面临成为警察国家的危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-08-04/humiliated-by-machado-maduro-arrests-2-000-in-crackdown-of-venezuela-opposition</guid>
