      <title>拜登助手敦促重启谈判以达成加沙停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/biden-aides-press-for-renewed-talks-to-get-gaza-cease-fire-done</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府一名高级官员呼吁以色列加倍就加沙停火进行谈判，并表示更广泛的地区冲突风险增加了与哈马斯达成协议的紧迫性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/biden-aides-press-for-renewed-talks-to-get-gaza-cease-fire-done</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 14:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
