      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:39:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国骚乱持续至周日，至少 100 人被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/police-make-at-least-90-arrests-as-far-right-protests-sweep-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，混乱局面蔓延至英国各城镇，极右翼抗议活动演变为暴力事件，警方逮捕了至少 100 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/police-make-at-least-90-arrests-as-far-right-protests-sweep-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 09:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方警告极右翼煽动街头暴力影响资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/uk-police-warn-far-right-fueled-street-violence-affects-resources-needed-to-investigate-other-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——英国首相基尔·斯塔默强烈谴责周日发生的针对一家收容寻求庇护者的酒店的袭击，称这是“极右翼暴徒行为”。此前，一场舞蹈课上发生了持刀伤人事件，造成三名女孩死亡，多人受伤，此后，英国多个城镇爆发了更多暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/uk-police-warn-far-right-fueled-street-violence-affects-resources-needed-to-investigate-other-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 09:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国下令关闭移动互联网以平息抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bangladesh-orders-mobile-internet-shutdown-to-quell-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周末再次爆发抗议活动导致 70 多人死亡，孟加拉国在三周内第二次加强了全国宵禁并下令关闭移动互联网服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bangladesh-orders-mobile-internet-shutdown-to-quell-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:40:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卫星图像显示液化天然气船停泊在受制裁的俄罗斯工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/satellite-images-show-first-lng-ship-at-sanctioned-russian-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据卫星图像显示，一艘大型船只上周停靠在俄罗斯位于北极的液化天然气出口工厂，这似乎是俄罗斯首次规避美国对该设施制裁的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/satellite-images-show-first-lng-ship-at-sanctioned-russian-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞浦路斯总统接受联合国邀请就数十年争端进行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/what-is-the-cyprus-problem-and-is-there-hope-for-a-solution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞浦路斯总统接受了联合国斡旋的会议邀请，该会议将试图重启关于分裂岛屿统一的谈判，但目前尚不清楚土耳其塞浦路斯领导人埃尔辛塔塔尔是否同意出席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/what-is-the-cyprus-problem-and-is-there-hope-for-a-solution</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 07:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚总统蒂努布称抗议活动旨在破坏政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/nigerian-president-calls-protests-that-killed-13-political</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布表示，上周导致至少 21 人死亡的示威活动有政治目的，目的是破坏他的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/nigerian-president-calls-protests-that-killed-13-political</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疑似胡塞导弹袭击集装箱船 两周内首次遇袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——当局周日称，也门胡塞叛军发动的导弹袭击击中了一艘穿越亚丁湾的悬挂利比里亚国旗的集装箱船，这是自以色列空袭以来该组织首次发动袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 01:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
